web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tate.org.uk/art/artists/frances-richards-1837\">\"Frances Richards biography\"</a>. Tate.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Frances+Richards+biography&amp;rft.pub=Tate&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tate.org.uk%2Fart%2Fartists%2Ffrances-richards-1837&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACeri+Richards\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.oxforddnb.com/templates/article.jsp?articleid=69557&amp;back=\"><i>Oxford Dictionary of National Biography</i></a>. Oxford University Press. 2004.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Oxford+Dictionary+of+National+Biography&amp;rft.pub=Oxford+University+Press&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.oxforddnb.com%2Ftemplates%2Farticle.jsp%3Farticleid%3D69557%26back%3D&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACeri+Richards\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Tate-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Tate_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tate.org.uk/art/artists/ceri-richards-1836\">\"Ceri Richards biography\"</a>. Tate<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">22 October</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Ceri+Richards+biography&amp;rft.pub=Tate&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ta